title: Oh Mai Vietnamese Sandwich Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vietnamese food menu, while primarily meat-based, also includes several vegan items like bun vermicelli noodle, lemongrass bean curd rice, tofu pho, vegan bahn mi sandwich, lemongrass bean curd bahn mi sandwich, veggie roll, and vegan roll - all of these are or can also be made gluten-free. Relaxed atmosphere.
